{"thag15.1:0.1":"Theragatha 15.1 ","thag15.1:0.2":"Solasakanipata ","thag15.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag15.1:0.4":"Annasikondannattheragatha ","thag15.1:1.1":"“Esa bhiyyo pasidami, ","thag15.1:1.2":"sutva dhammam maharasam; ","thag15.1:1.3":"Virago desito dhammo, ","thag15.1:1.4":"anupadaya sabbaso”. ","thag15.1:2.1":"“Bahuni loke citrani, ","thag15.1:2.2":"asmim pathavimandale; ","thag15.1:2.3":"Mathenti manne sankappam, ","thag15.1:2.4":"subham ragupasamhitam. ","thag15.1:3.1":"Rajamuhatanca vatena, ","thag15.1:3.2":"yatha meghopasammaye; ","thag15.1:3.3":"Evam sammanti sankappa, ","thag15.1:3.4":"yada pannaya passati. ","thag15.1:4.1":"Sabbe sankhara aniccati, ","thag15.1:4.2":"yada pannaya passati; ","thag15.1:4.3":"Atha nibbindati dukkhe, ","thag15.1:4.4":"esa maggo visuddhiya. ","thag15.1:5.1":"Sabbe sankhara dukkhati, ","thag15.1:5.2":"yada pannaya passati; ","thag15.1:5.3":"Atha nibbindati dukkhe, ","thag15.1:5.4":"esa maggo visuddhiya. ","thag15.1:6.1":"Sabbe dhamma anattati, ","thag15.1:6.2":"yada pannaya passati; ","thag15.1:6.3":"Atha nibbindati dukkhe, ","thag15.1:6.4":"esa maggo visuddhiya. ","thag15.1:7.1":"Buddhanubuddho yo thero, ","thag15.1:7.2":"kondanno tibbanikkamo; ","thag15.1:7.3":"Pahinajatimarano, ","thag15.1:7.4":"brahmacariyassa kevali. ","thag15.1:8.1":"Oghapaso dalhakhilo, ","thag15.1:8.2":"Pabbato duppadalayo; ","thag15.1:8.3":"Chetva khilanca pasanca, ","thag15.1:8.4":"Selam bhetvana dubbhidam; ","thag15.1:8.5":"Tinno parangato jhayi, ","thag15.1:8.6":"Mutto so marabandhana. ","thag15.1:9.1":"Uddhato capalo bhikkhu, ","thag15.1:9.2":"mitte agamma papake; ","thag15.1:9.3":"Samsidati mahoghasmim, ","thag15.1:9.4":"umiya patikujjito. ","thag15.1:10.1":"Anuddhato acapalo, ","thag15.1:10.2":"nipako samvutindriyo; ","thag15.1:10.3":"Kalyanamitto medhavi, ","thag15.1:10.4":"dukkhassantakaro siya. ","thag15.1:11.1":"Kalapabbangasankaso, ","thag15.1:11.2":"kiso dhamanisanthato; ","thag15.1:11.3":"Mattannu annapanasmim, ","thag15.1:11.4":"adinamanaso naro. ","thag15.1:12.1":"Phuttho damsehi makasehi, ","thag15.1:12.2":"arannasmim brahavane; ","thag15.1:12.3":"Nago sangamasiseva, ","thag15.1:12.4":"sato tatradhivasaye. ","thag15.1:13.1":"Nabhinandami maranam, ","thag15.1:13.2":"… pe ","thag15.1:13.3":"… ","thag15.1:13.4":"nibbisam bhatako yatha. ","thag15.1:14.1":"Nabhinandami maranam, ","thag15.1:14.2":"… pe ","thag15.1:14.3":"… ","thag15.1:14.4":"sampajano patissato. ","thag15.1:15.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thag15.1:15.2":"… pe ","thag15.1:15.3":"… ","thag15.1:15.4":"bhavanetti samuhata. ","thag15.1:16.1":"Yassa catthaya pabbajito, ","thag15.1:16.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thag15.1:16.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","thag15.1:16.4":"kim me saddhiviharina”ti. ","thag15.1:16.5":"… Annasikondanno thero …. "}